msgstr "Опције"

#: src/toolbox/transform/warp-transform.xml:64(title)
#: src/toolbox/transform/unified-transform.xml:190(title)
#: src/toolbox/transform/transform-3d.xml:73(title)
#: src/toolbox/transform/shear.xml:87(title)
